reviews.text: Executive chef Hideaki Nagaya, whose impressive portfolio include being head chef of the Michelin starred L'Effervescence, and NARISAWA before that in Tokyo. If to try to classify his cuisine it would be "French fusion Kaiseki" at this new restaurant of his. Highlights of the meal are Chawanmushi (steamed egg) with uni emulsion and hairy crab meat, uni espuma cracker, pot rice with miso black cod, and finally the wagyu from Kagoshima was just perfect！

reviews.text: I got the smashed mangos with jasmine. The drink was good but the boba pearls were terrible - hard and tough.
Cute interior design, delicious food and drinks, great price for HK island. The seating is a little bit uncomfortable but still okay.
Indoor dining area, front row having flying insects very ignoring, make me itchy. Tea taste good.
I love the Matcha bubble tea so muchaaa!!  Cutesy branding. love it. The grilled cheese is also really nice.

Colorful flamingos decorate the small bubble tea shop to provide for an excellent Instagram worthy experience. Throngs of single women descend on this place to order exactly one cup of bubble tea and one bowl of ramen noodles. They then setup the cup and bowl at the small table and snap a selfie to show the world how special they are.

Being distracted by themselves, they likely failed to notice that the tea isn't all that good. The various teas were fairly bitter. They use very thick disposable plastic cups that will surely pollute the beaches a million years into the future.

The ramen noodle is soaked in oily msg laden soup base. The bowl is very small, so don't expect to eat a real meal here. This is purely designed to be a photography pitstop.

Enjoy the bitter tea. Temper your expectations. Publish those bright pink photos and score some karma!

reviews.text:
終於有間新飲品店不只是飲品店 🤘🏿 今次呢間新飲品係以紅鶴做主題，代表咩 🤷🏿‍♂️ 單身既朋友有福了，可以脫單了，門口有隻非常吸睛既大大大紅鶴，可以攬足一個鐘，瘋狂攬攬，瘋狂錫錫 🤤 蜜運中既朋友亦都有福了，可以一齊拖手仔同小鶴影蜜運照，況如置身蜜運中，感受一下初戀既感覺 😳 岩岩甩拖既朋友最有福了，因為呢隻小鶴其實係一隻大水泡黎既，實行黎個水泡計劃同小鶴扮蜜運 🤤🤤🤤
返返黎重點先，而家每日 4 點至 8 點買野飲都係買 1 送 1，超級抵飲，飲品大多數都係 $1x - $2x 一杯，為返起都係 $10 一杯，超級呀媽太平賣呀 🤘🏿
呢到既野飲都係以健康為主，主打都係茶類飲品，想飲清淡啲既有 #茉莉毛尖綠茶，茶味比較清香，唔會太濃，想加奶蓋或者珍珠要加 $5，奶蓋香滑度中等，但珍珠好好食好有咬口 🤤
想飲清新既有 #多果油切烏龍，即係水果茶，呢杯既水果茶既果味同茶味既比例都幾大對比，烏龍茶既茶味真你好濃 😂 果味就相對上好弱，但始終水果茶都唔會差得去邊，整體都 ok 🤘🏿
最正既最一定要飲一定係 #雲南胎菊普洱，個菊香茶味真係不得了 🤤 而且胎菊有清熱明目減肥作用，真係一舉幾得 🤘🏿 加埋奶蓋珍珠真係冇得頂 🤘🏿 近期飲過既飲品最喜愛之一 🤤
重點 P.S. 小鶴而家係我既鶴，雖然我已經同佢大戰左 300 回，打足 3 分 33 秒既茄倫，但係我都好願意 happy share 比大家，希望大家對小鶴溫柔一點 🤤🤤🤤
